---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title='Contenido1'>
  <article
    slot='content'
    class='flex items-center justify-center max-w-screen xl:mt-0 mt-40 sm:mb-4 lg:mb-4 mx-4 inset-0 bg-[#e0dddd] dark:bg-[#18191d] relative'
  >
  <div class="flex flex-col bg-[#e0dddd] dark:bg-[#18191d] lg:mt-8">
    <main class="flex flex-col md:flex-row sm:flex-row flex-1 overflow-hidden">
      <article class="prose prose-gray mx-auto p-6 max-w-screen max-h-screen md:w-3/4 dark:prose-invert">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight lg:text-5xl lg:leading-[3.5rem] dark:text-white">
          The Ultimate Guide to Shopping Online
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd]">By Jane Doe | Posted on August 24, 2024</p>
        <p class="text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd]">
          Online shopping is a form of electronic commerce which allows consumers to directly buy goods or services
          from a seller over the Internet using a web browser or a mobile app...
        </p>
        <img
          src="/placeholder.svg"
          alt="Blog post image"
          width="800"
          height="400"
          class="aspect-video object-cover"
        />
        <p class="text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd]">
          ...As of 2020, customers can shop online using a range of different computers and devices, including desktop
          computers, laptops, tablet computers, smartphones, and smart speakers...
        </p>
      </article>
      <aside class="w-full h-screen md:w-1/5 p-6 border-l border-black dark:border-white">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Related Products</h2>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
              <img
                src="/placeholder.svg"
                alt="Product image"
                width="80"
                height="80"
                class="aspect-square object-cover"
              />
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd]">Product Name</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd] ">$99.99</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
              <img
                src="/placeholder.svg"
                alt="Product image"
                width="80"
                height="80"
                class="aspect-square object-cover"
              />
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd]">Product Name</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd]">$99.99</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>        
      </aside>
    </main>
  </div>

  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  @media (width<1480px) {
    aside {
    display: none;
    }
}
@media (width:1280px) {
    .xl\:mt-0 {
        margin-top: 50px;
    }
}
</style>




